1.1
log
@New sim testsuite for Fujitsu FRV. Contributed by Red Hat.
@
text
@d19 18
d52 1
a52 1
	stdfi		fr1,@@(sp,0)	; misaligned reg -- slot I0
d57 1
a57 1
	lddfi		@@(sp,0),fr9	; misaligned reg -- slot I1
@

